item.title: CVE-2023-4016|2024-08-02T07:17:10.954Z -- linux -- linux%20kernal
item.description: Under some circumstances, this weakness allows a user who has access to run the “ps” utility on a machine, the ability to write almost unlimited amounts of unfiltered data into the process heap.
